summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 80E, Page 188 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Block 26 of Dunlap's Plat of Land on Lake Washington from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 500) Zone, and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (C.F. 289840, Petition of Euel O. Atkinson).
